      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "NOVA REIGN (8) was below best latest but did hit the frame in quick time two back when second (29.95) at this track in a Grade 5. Safe beginner but wide box to overcome and will need some luck. Likely to improve sharply this time. IRINKA WAYNE (7) is having his first start around this track. Comes here a last start placegetter at Maitland in a Grade 5 (22.49). Has good speed and will be prominent from out wide. Expected to be in the finish again. MR. BOMBASTIC (6) slotted in just off the lead from the wide draw last start and boxed on to finish second (29.75) at this track in a Grade 5 over 515m. Ran one of the fastest times on the program last start despite finishing in the minors. Expected to feature again. MISS BANSKY (4) should be thereabouts after filling a top-three spot most recently.",
